==Images==
Upload an image using the [[Main/en/special:upload|upload file]] link found in the main menu.

Use this code to add an image to the article:
<pre>[[File:en/.filename|frame|none|caption]]</pre>

Example:
<pre>[[File:en/Longerbridges.png|frame|none|Longer bridges]]</pre>
Result:
[[File:en/Longerbridges.png|frame|none|Longer bridges]]

*Also see [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:Extended_image_syntax Extended image syntax] on Wikipedia.

